OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLiverpool City Council     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffailings over Everton loan 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F'could cost thousands'     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thousands of pounds could be written   
OL,6, off by Liverpool City Council over a   
OL,7, deal to lend Everton money for a new   
OL,8, stadium, a report has said.            
OL,10,FThe document said the authority        
OL,11,Fincurred a significant cost looking    
OL,12,Finto the possibility of a loan to the  
OL,13,Ffootball club without formal approval. 
OL,15,FGovernment-appointed commissioners     
OL,16,Foverseeing some departments said there 
OL,17,Fhad been a "failure of governance".    
OL,19,FThey added that as a result, some costs
OL,20,Fwere irrecoverable.                    
